BEGIN_PGML
Here is a definition: [` x \: \Box \: y = 2x+3y `].  Read it and use it to:  
Find [` [$a] \: \Box \: [$b] \: =`] [____________]{Compute("$c")}

Find [`c \:\Box \: x \:= `] [_____________]{Compute("2*c+3*x")}

